#: ../../admincli/activereplica.rst:11
msgid ""
"The |product| architecture is mostly based on services that make nodes "
"*stateless*, redundant, and clustered *by design*.  The only **stateful**"
" service is the *Mailstore*, due to the fundamental role it plays in "
"storing metadata, binary blobs, and connection cache."
msgstr ""

#: ../../admincli/activereplica.rst:16
msgid ""
