"Spam Delivery** tolerance is by default (i.e., the *Medium* value) *33%*,"
" while the **Tolerance for Spam Blocking** is *75%*. This means that a "
"e-mail with a spam score of ~6.6 will be marked as spam email, while with"
" spam score 15 will be immediately be deleted. Changing the value to "
"*Low* or *High* will reduce or raise the threshold to mark or delete spam"
" e-mails."
