#: ../../_includes/_usage/chats.rst:62
msgid ""
"To create a new meeting, click the :bdg-primary-line:`CREATE ROOM` "
"button, then enter a name. You will be automatically assigned the role of"
" **Owner**. Besides being a :ref:`Moderator <chats_moderators_in_rooms>`,"
" an owner can not be removed and is the solely person that can delete a "
"Virtual Room."
msgstr ""

#: ../../_includes/_usage/chats.rst:68
msgid ""
"In the left-hand side column, all meetings are shown, divided into "
"**Ongoing Meetings** and **Scheduled meetings**. For each of them, a few "
"buttons are shown, to join or delete a virtual room, to copy and share "
"the virtual room's link and to change the link."
