#: ../../_includes/_usage/mails.rst:235
msgid "Trash Folder"
msgstr ""

#: ../../_includes/_usage/mails.rst:237
msgid ""
"The trash folder is a special folder in which e-mails marked for deletion"
" are temporary stored, in case they need to be recovered. An e-mail in "
"the Trash folder will be automatically deleted after a period equivalent "
"to the retention time, by default **30 days**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../_includes/_usage/mails.rst:245
msgid "Junk Folder"
msgstr ""

#: ../../_includes/_usage/mails.rst:247
msgid ""
"Like the *trash folder*, this is a special folder in which e-mails that "
"are wither marked as **spam**, or otherwise are unsolicited or undesired,"
" are stored."
msgstr ""

#: ../../_includes/_usage/mails.rst:251
msgid ""
