"automatically infer whether an e-mail is legit or not and mark it as "
"spam. However, in case you think an e-mail is spam but was not processed,"
" it can be manually marked as spam by right-clicking it and selecting "
"*Mark as spam*. Also that vice-versa is valid: an e-mail in the *Junk* "
"folder (i.e., recognised as spam) can be marked as *not spam*: it will "
"land in the **Inbox**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../_includes/_usage/mails.rst:259
msgid ""
"All the content of the junk folder helps the anti-spam engine to learn "
"and improve its results."
msgstr ""

