msgstr ""

#: ../../_includes/_usage/mails.rst:264
msgid ""
"A *massive e-mail sending* is the process of sending legitimate e-mails "
"to a large number of e-mail addresses, often used for marketing purposes "
"and using a specific software or online service for this purpose."
msgstr ""

#: ../../_includes/_usage/mails.rst:269
msgid ""
